    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved\u2014I've always made sure to keep up with the maintenance so it runs like a dream! It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for something reliable and stylish that still feels fresh on the road. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner very happy. Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
