    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L straight-six, delivering high-revving linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The double-VANOS system has been serviced, ensuring optimal cam phasing across the entire RPM range. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to an M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings to address common subframe concerns, and the suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics for exceptional lateral grip. Recent fluid analysis confirms the mechanical integrity of the rod bearings. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior shows honest wear consistent with its mileage, while the interior maintains its driver-centric ergonomics. A purist-spec machine ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
