    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Lexus RX 350 in Eminent White Pearl. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and reflects consistent pride of ownership. The exterior retains a deep, brilliant gloss; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway driving, the body is straight and free of major blemishes. Inside, the Parchment leather interior remains supple and smoke-free. The cabin electronics, including the 12.3-inch navigation display and the premium audio system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a documented service history. The 3.5L V6 engine delivers smooth power, and the transmission shifts effortlessly. It recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection, and the Michelin tires have plenty of tread remaining. This is a solid, honest luxury SUV that offers a perfect balance of comfort and reliability for its next owner.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
