    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid condition\u2014super clean, well-loved, and it still drives like a total dream! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with all the regular maintenance, so it\u2019s completely ready for its next big adventure. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks sharp on the road, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love to see it go to a great new home, so feel free to message me with any questions!",
