    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its high-revving nature and individual throttle bodies. This example retains its crisp throttle response and linear power delivery, benefiting from a documented VANOS service and subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for chassis rigidity. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. Riding on a well-sorted suspension with refreshed bushings, it delivers the communicative steering feel expected of this platform. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the powertrain remains robust, providing an authentic, analog driving experience.",
